@startuml
'!theme plain
autonumber

title Security Evaluation Tool - Conceptual Populate DB Flow

actor User
participant "CLI" as CLI
participant "DocumentLoader"
participant "VectorStore"

User -> CLI: populate-db
CLI -> DocumentLoader: load and split all documents in configured directory
activate DocumentLoader
DocumentLoader --> CLI: chunks with metadata for all documents
deactivate DocumentLoader
CLI -> VectorStore: add all chunks to vector store
activate VectorStore
VectorStore --> CLI: IDs for all chunks stored in Postgres
deactivate VectorStore


@enduml
